114
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,625
Seperti yang anda inginkan.

115
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,125
Selepas anda mati,

116
00:06:04,625 --> 00:06:07,625
Tujuh Bilah Syaitan Syurga Songsang Keluarga Chen

